  "title": "ISic003202. Fragment of an honorific inscription",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prado, 2023-05-09</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ELIV[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span> pra]ep(osito) <span data-text=\"d\">d</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span> nume?]ro eq[uitum? <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span> via?]e <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Traianae\">Trai[anae?</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prado, 2023-05-09</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ELIV[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>...]EP<span data-text=\"d\">D</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>....]ROEQ[.....<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>...]E<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Traianae\">TRAI[....</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003202_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-05-09\" src=\"ISic003202_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003202.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-05-09\" src=\"ISic003202-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Prado from autopsy</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Both Libertini and Manganaro suggested reading Legio Secunda Traiana in the fourth line, but a position such as 'curator viae Traianae' is at least equally possible.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 1955.0192 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a></li><li> Libertini NSA 1953 361 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a></li></ul>  <ul><li> Manganaro 1988 40 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427</a></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Lines 2-4  70  Interlineation line 1 to 2  20-25  Interlineation line 2 to 4  30  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence </div>",
